dct_description_sm: Large corrections Mar. 73.; Relief shown by hachures, soundings, and spot heights.; Includes 6 cross sections and 6 insets: Caldeira of Graciosa -- [Gomez Bay] -- Praya of Graciosa -- [Monte Brazil, Cidade de Angra] -- Praya de Terceira -- [Cabras].; North oriented to the upper left.
37 x 44 centimeters and 17 x 19 centimeters, on sheet 49 x 65 centimeters
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
